title: Eni Reports Natural Gas Discovery off Egyptian Coast
text:
Milanâ€”Eni SpA said Sunday it made a massive natural-gas discovery off the coast of Egypt in what the Italian oil-and-gas company is calling the largest-ever find in the Mediterranean Sea.
